# Space Cowboy — Code Mode Briefing

## What This Is
Browser-based 3D space debris cleanup game. Three.js r170, vanilla ES6 modules, zero build tools. Player commands the V5 "Crossbow" ADR satellite: deploy autonomous arms to capture 50 debris objects. ~22K+ LOC across 46 modules.

## Architecture (read ARCHITECTURE.md §1 for full module map)

```
js/main.js              — Bootstrap + game loop (~520 LOC)
js/core/                — Constants.js (all tuning), EventBus.js (pub/sub), Events.js (event names), GameState.js (FSM)
js/scene/               — SceneManager (renderer+bloom), Earth (3-layer), Starfield, SunLight (sun/moon/flares)
js/entities/            — PlayerSatellite, ArmManager→ArmUnit (20-state FSM), DebrisField (instanced), OrbitalMechanics
js/systems/             — 24 modules: GameFlowManager, InputManager, CameraSystem, AudioSystem, ResourceSystem,
                          ScoringSystem, PowerDistribution, SensorSystem, ForgeSystem, CargoSystem, CommsSystem,
                          AutopilotSystem, CollisionAvoidanceSystem, TrawlManager, LassoSystem, TutorialSystem,
                          CodexSystem, SpaceWeatherSystem, ConjunctionSystem, KesslerSystem, RewardSystem,
                          SubsystemEvents, TargetSelector, PersistenceManager
js/ui/                  — HUD.js (coordinator), hud/StatusPanel+TargetPanel+CommsPanel, NavSphere, OrbitMFD,
                          TargetReticle, DebrisWireframe, DockingReticle, CodexViewerUI, ShopScreen, etc.
js/test/                — TestRunner.js (micro-framework), run-tests.js (entry), 9 test files, 44 suites
```

## Key Patterns
- **EventBus** — All module communication via Events.js constants. Zero raw event strings.
- **Constants.js** — ALL tuning knobs. ~840 LOC. Change gameplay balance here.
- **GameState FSM** — MENU→BRIEFING→ORBITAL_VIEW→APPROACH→INTERACTION→SHOP→GAME_OVER→WIN
- **Canvas2D overlays** — 5 files use DPI-scaled Canvas2D (TargetReticle, NavSphere, OrbitMFD, DebrisWireframe, DockingReticle)
- **No build tools** — `./start.sh` runs Python HTTP server on port 8081. Import maps in index.html.
- **Singleton exports** — targetSelector, kesslerSystem, trawlManager (imported directly, not via _refs)
- **GameFlowManager._refs** — 6 remaining: player, debrisField, armManager, cameraSystem, shopScreen, resourceSystem

