## Testing
Zero-dependency micro-framework in `js/test/TestRunner.js` (describe/it/assert). Run:
```
node js/test/run-tests.js    # or ./test.sh
```
- 9 test files, 44 suites, 278 tests — all passing
- Tests target Node-safe modules only (no THREE.js, no DOM)
- Browser tests: open `test.html`
- Add new test files to `js/test/run-tests.js` imports

For manual gameplay testing: `./start.sh`, open http://localhost:8081.

## Files That Should NOT Be Modified Without Understanding
- `js/core/Constants.js` — All balance tuning. Changes cascade everywhere.
- `js/systems/GameFlowManager.js` — State transitions, 26+ EventBus handlers. Complex wiring.
- `js/entities/ArmUnit.js` — 20-state FSM. State transitions are fragile.
